So what's happening for most people

00:06:51.093 --> 00:06:53.093
the idea of going to school,

00:06:53.347 --> 00:06:58.005
getting a job, working hard,
saving money, getting out of debt,

00:06:58.084 --> 00:07:01.171
buying your house because it's
an asset and investing for a long term.

